comments: The senior essay is the best part of the lit major.
TAKE IT IN THE FALL! (Seriously.)Still want to take it in the spring?DON'T!Have you already done your senior essay?Oh, that's funny. 'Cause I have.And I'm telling you: TAKE IT IN THE FALL!
Great opportunity to explore a topic you really care about.

I had a great experience writing my senior essay. My thesis advisor was absolutely wonderful, and I think this was a key in having a positive essay-writing process. It might be better to have a few meetings with Professor Skorupa early on, but overall the senior essay process went smoothly.
